moji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台服已經有一班香港人 如果有興趣就入月夜幻想曲啦 港人開的 其實唔算死城 都幾多人玩</blockquote><br />\n我都好想重玩<br />\n不過真係有心無力<br />\n玩個陣仲係學生<br />\n每日用幾個鐘去打副本刷職刷聲望<br />\n依家出到黎做野連打一場英雄副本既時間都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 月夜幻想曲個名好熟<br />\n以前我玩個陣好似都係大公會黎"},{"pid":"d680d0792284dc8791176e4218d2d208de9f9792","tid":353643,"uid":3562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加加埋埋應該玩左3年左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n部舊機仲有d相有無人想睇下懷念下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87de058682c376e086650dcd91abe695ff1a595c","tid":353643,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加加埋埋應該玩左3年左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n部舊機仲有d相有無人想睇下懷念下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1db2c161849b0a94a5065c79dfd6c4d23bc008","tid":353643,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依加仲有一批人玩台服 台服承諾永久唔會摺 請安心玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會有人想組隊重玩<br />\n不過睇巴哈版都好似死城咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></b